{{Lunisolar November}} '''November 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and its day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenkyō|ja|貞享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1685|ja|1685|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|January 3|ja|1月3日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} revised the old Senmyō calendar into the Yamato calendar (later known as the {{ill|Tenkyō|ja|貞享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} calendar). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 28|ja|12月28日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The customs offices at Nagasaki, Yokohama, and Hakodate were renamed as customs. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1872nd year 12月28日) – A decree for universal conscription was issued, prompting uprisings in various regions.
== Births == * {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1866|ja|1866|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|August 19|ja|8月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – [[中村不折]], a Western-style painter and calligrapher (died [[1943]]).
