{{Lunisolar November|qq=}}
'''November 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|12=draft}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} and its day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Tenkyō|ja|貞享|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1685|ja|1685|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|January 3|ja|1月3日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shibukawa Harumi|ja|渋川春海|qq=|12=draft}} revised the old Senmyō calendar into the Yamato calendar (later known as the {{ill|Tenkyō|ja|貞享|qq=|12=draft}} calendar).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1872|ja|1872|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|December 28|ja|12月28日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The customs offices at Nagasaki, Yokohama, and Hakodate were renamed as customs.
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} 1872nd year 12月28日) – A decree for universal conscription was issued, prompting uprisings in various regions.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Keiō|ja|慶応|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|1866|ja|1866|qq=|12=draft}} {{ill|August 19|ja|8月19日|qq=|12=draft}}) – [[中村不折]], a Western-style painter and calligrapher (died [[1943]]).

== Deaths ==
* [[Empress Jitō]] 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[696]] {{ill|August 13|ja|8月13日|qq=|12=draft}}) – [[高市皇子]], a prince of Emperor Tenmu (born ~654?).
* {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|qq=|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1824]] {{ill|August 4|ja|8月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – [[Maeda Seihiro]], 12th lord of the Kaga Domain (born [[1782]]).

