'''November 28''' is the 28th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Tomobiki|WD=Q96759840|1=tomobiki}}{{efn|ja|友引|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}{{efn|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q9418169}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Jōkyō|en|Jōkyō|WD=Q1146221|lt=Tenkyō|1=Jōkyō}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1685|en|1685|WD=Q7660|lt=1685|1=1685}} {{ill|January 3|en|January 3|WD=Q2156|lt=January 3|1=January 3}}) – {{ill|Shibukawa Shunkai|en|Shibukawa Shunkai|WD=Q786877|lt=Shibukawa Harumi|1=Shibukawa Shunkai}} revised the old Senmyō calendar into the Yamato calendar (later known as the {{ill|Jōkyō|en|Jōkyō|WD=Q1146221|lt=Tenkyō|1=Jōkyō}} calendar).
* {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|WD=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1872|en|1872|WD=Q7753|lt=1872|1=1872}} {{ill|December 28|en|December 28|WD=Q2832|lt=December 28|1=December 28}}) – The customs offices at Nagasaki, Yokohama, and Hakodate were renamed as customs.
* {{ill|Meiji era|en|Meiji era|WD=Q3125096|lt=Meiji era|1=Meiji era}} 5th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} 1872nd year 12月28日) – A decree for universal conscription was issued, prompting uprisings in various regions.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Keiō|en|Keiō|WD=Q776775|lt=Keiō|1=Keiō}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1866|en|1866|WD=Q7712|lt=1866|1=1866}} {{ill|August 19|en|August 19|WD=Q2829|lt=August 19|1=August 19}}) – [[中村不折]], a Western-style painter and calligrapher (died {{ill|1943|en|1943|WD=Q18623|lt=1943|1=1943}}).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Empress Jitō|en|Empress Jitō|WD=Q232026|lt=Empress Jitō|1=Empress Jitō}} 10th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|WD=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|696|en|696|WD=Q23486|lt=696|1=696}} {{ill|August 13|en|August 13|WD=Q2776|lt=August 13|1=August 13}}) – [[高市皇子]], a prince of Emperor Tenmu (born ~654?).
* {{ill|Bunsei|en|Bunsei|WD=Q1327119|lt=Bunsei|1=Bunsei}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|WD=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1824|en|1824|WD=Q6994|lt=1824|1=1824}} {{ill|August 4|en|August 4|WD=Q2784|lt=August 4|1=August 4}}) – [[Maeda Seihiro]], 12th lord of the Kaga Domain (born {{ill|1782|en|1782|WD=Q7740|lt=1782|1=1782}}).

